* 补充泪液：人工泪液（尽量选择不含或较少防腐剂的药水）<ref name="#2">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nhs.uk/Conditions/Dry-eye-syndrome/Pages/Treatment.aspx |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-01-17 |archive-date=2017-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171001135406/http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/dry-eye-syndrome/Pages/Treatment.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>（主要成分有：硫酸软骨素、玻璃酸钠、羧甲基纤维素钠等）
